# Three MDI window types:
#
# Query        (X)
# ... use a vertical splitter, Query at the top List of cards below ...
# ... details of query|list of matching cards if any ...
# 0 cards match
#
# Name (of Card)  (X)
# Body
# ...
# [Boxes          v] # boxes this card belongs to
# [Linked Cards   v] # cards this card is linked to
#
# Box           (X)
# Name
# ...

# NOTE Markup is CommonMark

